weight tagging along.

13
00:00:37,371 --> 00:00:39,998
[MASH groans] Then I'd better
show you what I'm made of!

14
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:43,710
They call me "Mash the Hero"
back in my hometown of Nakashi!

15
00:00:43,752 --> 00:00:46,255
Whatevs. Sounds
like a crock o' shi.

16
00:00:46,296 --> 00:00:48,090
[MASH]
That's Nakashi, jerk!

17
00:00:48,131 --> 00:00:48,924
[gasps]

18
00:00:48,966 --> 00:00:50,175
[ELULU]
Don't try to fight him, Mash!

19
00:00:50,217 --> 00:00:52,010
[KNIGHT CAPTAIN 04A]
Hey! What's going on over here?

20
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:54,972
Who would dare to desecrate
this holy church into ruin?

21
00:00:55,013 --> 00:00:56,515
[KNIGHT 04A]
No, Sister, are you hurt?

22
00:00:56,557 --> 00:00:58,559
[KNIGHT CAPTAIN 04A]
You! Explain yourselves!

23
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,810
If I sense deception,
I'll haul you in...

24
00:00:59,851 --> 00:01:01,562
