25
00:01:01,603 --> 00:01:04,481
I can tell you how it all
broke down. Oh, wait, too soon?

26
00:01:04,523 --> 00:01:06,858
[SISTER] The truth is,
there was a horrible creature

27
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:09,111
that disguised
itself as a priest.

28
00:01:09,152 --> 00:01:11,613
Were they responsible
for this sinful misdeed?

29
00:01:11,655 --> 00:01:12,948
[SISTER]
I'm still rather shaken,

30
00:01:12,990 --> 00:01:15,576
so the exact details
are vague, but yes.

31
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:19,580
I'm positive it was that undead
brute who destroyed the chapel.

32
00:01:19,621 --> 00:01:21,790
One thing I do
remember clearly‐‐

33
00:01:21,832 --> 00:01:23,208
it said 10,000 more

34
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:25,711
of its ungodly ilk
would come to join it.

35
00:01:25,752 --> 00:01:28,422
They've already overtaken
Krain Castle heading south.

36
00:01:28,463 --> 00:01:30,048
Who could've
imagined such numbers?

37
00:01:30,090 --> 00:01:31,967
[SISTER]
Hold fast to your faith, sir.

38
00:01:32,009 --> 00:01:34,720
You see, God has
not forsaken us yet.

39
00:01:34,761 --> 00:01:35,762
Don't you worry.

40
00:01:35,804 --> 00:01:39,141
After all, the heavens have
sent us a divine goddess,

41
00:01:39,182 --> 00:01:41,685
as well as a blessed
hero with great strength.

42
00:01:41,727 --> 00:01:44,771
