Dragonkin blood in their veins.

43
00:01:44,813 --> 00:01:47,649
[gasps] Please,
forgive my rudeness!

44
00:01:47,691 --> 00:01:48,734
Let's start over.

45
00:01:48,775 --> 00:01:51,320
We're knights of the empire,
sent to defend Seimul,

46
00:01:51,361 --> 00:01:53,488
sworn to defeat
the Undead Horde!

47
00:01:53,530 --> 00:01:57,659
Sir Hero, we humbly request
that you fight alongside us!

48
00:01:57,701 --> 00:01:59,077
[SEIYA]
How much you got?

49
00:01:59,119 --> 00:02:00,579
