51
00:02:02,247 --> 00:02:04,833
Hold on, Seiya! You think now
is the best time for this?

52
00:02:04,875 --> 00:02:07,669
Pipe down. I learned
a new move recently.

53
00:02:07,711 --> 00:02:10,464
It's one that requires a
fairly hefty amount of capital.

54
00:02:10,505 --> 00:02:13,258
