57
00:02:18,138 --> 00:02:19,931
[SEIYA] Cool, bro.
I'll just need that in writing.

58
00:02:19,973 --> 00:02:22,517
Uh, one moment!

59
00:02:22,559 --> 00:02:24,645
There's 200 knights
on their way here.

60
00:02:24,686 --> 00:02:26,396
Don't you want our help?
We're the imperial‐‐

61
00:02:26,438 --> 00:02:27,230
[SEIYA]
Hard pass.

62
00:02:27,272 --> 00:02:29,274
Wait, whaddaya
mean "hard pass"?

63
00:02:29,316 --> 00:02:32,152
[SEIYA] I'll bet this town has
a few stragglers lurking around.

64
00:02:32,194 --> 00:02:35,030
You guys should stay
here and protect 'em.

65
00:02:35,072 --> 00:02:37,699
Yo. Are you paying
attention, Mashed Potato?

66
00:02:37,741 --> 00:02:41,244
Hey, my name is Mash the Hero!
Stop mispronouncing everything!

67
00:02:41,286 --> 00:02:42,871
[SEIYA] If you're not
going back to crock o' shi,

68
00:02:42,913 --> 00:02:45,707
then help out the knights,
or whatever isn't around me.

69
00:02:45,749 --> 00:02:47,167
Well, what do we do now?

70
00:02:47,209 --> 00:02:50,379
Ha! Definitely not
whatever that jerk says!

71
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:51,922
Ahh!

72
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:55,217
[ELULU]
