be studying sword moves,

190
00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:39,793
not torturing the guy.

191
00:07:39,834 --> 00:07:41,836
[SEIYA] Well, I think
that took out most of them.

192
00:07:41,878 --> 00:07:43,129
But I'm not done‐‐

193
00:07:43,171 --> 00:07:45,423
not until I launch
another meteor first.

194
00:07:45,465 --> 00:07:47,884
[RISTA]
Awesome. Talk about gains!

195
00:07:47,926 --> 00:07:49,761
That's strong enough to
take out a Heavenly King

196
00:07:49,803 --> 00:07:51,972
like Deathmagla for sure!

197
00:07:52,013 --> 00:07:54,391
Nothing against Mash and Elulu,

198
00:07:54,432 --> 00:07:57,060
but this boy can do
bad all by himself!

199
00:07:57,102 --> 00:07:58,812
All he has to do is
make that happen

200
00:07:58,853 --> 00:08:01,690
