and then our job is done!

201
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:02,899
Piece of cake!

202
00:08:02,941 --> 00:08:06,778
[RISTA chuckling]

203
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,405
‐‐[SEIYA groans]
‐‐[RISTA] Hmm?

204
00:08:08,446 --> 00:08:10,573
