[SEIYA]
I may have gone too hardcore.

206
00:08:12,450 --> 00:08:14,703
I need to recover for a while.

207
00:08:14,744 --> 00:08:15,954
I gotcha, hero.

208
00:08:15,996 --> 00:08:18,665
Let's head back to town and
get you to the inn right away.

209
00:08:19,708 --> 00:08:22,419
[RISTA] He fired off two
of those spells in a row.

210
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:25,255
That must've eaten
up most of his MP.

211
00:08:25,296 --> 00:08:29,175
[groans] I started
out with 15,000 MP.

212
00:08:29,217 --> 00:08:31,094
There's just 13,000 left!

213
00:08:31,136 --> 00:08:35,765
[RISTA] Huh?! You barely
used any of it, you hoarder!

214
00:08:41,104 --> 00:08:45,191
[ELULU panting]

215
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:52,741
