home to your village.

219
00:08:58,621 --> 00:09:00,832
That's what worries me.
He would've told me first.

220
00:09:00,874 --> 00:09:02,375
I'm sure he's doing fine.

221
00:09:02,417 --> 00:09:03,626
The chances are slim to none

222
00:09:03,668 --> 00:09:05,336
that he'll run into
any real trouble.

223
00:09:05,378 --> 00:09:08,089
Especially now that the
undead baddies are gone.

224
00:09:08,131 --> 00:09:10,759
It's because of that
hero! Isn't he cool?

225
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,385
I wouldn't go that far.

226
00:09:12,427 --> 00:09:15,555
He won't stop nerding out
over this new Synthesis skill.

227
00:09:15,597 --> 00:09:18,141
