away in his quarters.

230
00:09:21,728 --> 00:09:23,480
Let's drop by and
see what he's up to.

231
00:09:23,521 --> 00:09:25,231
‐‐[ELULU giggles]
‐‐[knocking]

232
00:09:26,691 --> 00:09:29,194
Seiya, I'm coming in! Ugh!

233
00:09:29,235 --> 00:09:30,236
